    },
    {
      "id": "handnote",
      "html": "<p>Very regular letters, with serifs and a moderately wide module. R and B are closed, P is slightly open. A has a horizontal serif across the top. Interpuncts are irregular, sometimes triangular.</p> Line 1-6  48 (initial I is 56)  Interlineation line 1 to 2    "
    },
